@startuml
title Αρχιτεκτονική Εφαρμογής – Clean Architecture

skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 12
  FontSize 13
  FontName Arial
}
skinparam arrow {
  Color #2C3E50
  FontSize 11
}
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "UI\n(Compose Screens)" as UI #AED6F1
rectangle "ViewModel" as VM #D2B4DE
rectangle "Domain\n(Use Cases / Repository)" as Domain #A9DFBF
rectangle "Data\n(Room DB / Repository Impl)" as Data #FAD7A0

UI    -down->  VM     : events / actions
VM    -down->  Domain : calls use cases
Domain -down-> Data   : reads / writes

Data   -up->   Domain : results / entities
Domain -up->   VM     : domain models
VM     -up->   UI     : UI state (StateFlow)

@enduml
